Gold Price in Hong Kong Up
HONG KONG , November 19 ( Xinhua ) -- The gold price in Hong Kong rose 30 HK dollars to close at 2,745 HK dollars a tael Thursday , according to Po Sang Bank , one of the major gold dealers in Hong Kong .
The gold price is equivalent to 297.53 U.S. dollars a troy ounce , 3.87 U.S. dollars up from the previous close at Thursday 's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar against 7.7445 HK dollars .
